container_info.post_install_tip:
Here's how our add-on works:
- Find your perfect image using the search tool or by browsing our categories
- Click the image you like from the results
- Use "Preview in sheet" to see the preview image
- Click "Use in sheet" to license the image

name: Dreamstime Stock Photos
description: Enhance your documents with free, public domain (CC0 license), Royalty Free and Editorial stock images, fast and easy.
